	<h3 class="t-center p-l-15 p-r-15 p-t-3 title-font" style="color:black; font-size:200%;">
		Distribution of homeless people by age in 2011 and 2016
	</h3>
	<br>

	<!-- 第一行 -->
	<section style="margin-top:0; padding-top:0; padding-bottom: 100px;">
		<div class="container-fluid" style="height: 80%;">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6 embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
					<iframe frameborder="1" border="4" scrolling="no" class="embed-responsive-item" src="/stylesheets/1.html" allowfullscreen> </iframe>
				</div>
				
				<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6">
					<p style="text-align:justify">
						<br> Homelessness strikes to wide demography of people. There is no fixed age of homelessness. There are numerous reasons for becoming homeless. Often it is because of domestic violence, verbal or physical abuse, bankruptcy, eviction notice for not being able to pay the rent etc. The adjacent graph has been created from the dataset released by the <strong>Australian Bureau of Statistics in 2016</strong>. It shows the number of homeless people lying in different range.
						<br/>
						<br/> From the graph, it can be clearly stated that more than 5000 people from 25-34 years of age accounted for homelessness in 2016. The number increased by around 1000 from 2011. In addition, children of age less than 12 accounted for the second-largest group of homeless people. Around 3500 kids were found to be homeless in 2016. On the contrary, senior citizens of age 75 and above accounted suffered less homelessness. The difference in homelessness from 2011 and 2016 is less significant when considering the people from 35 – 75 years of age. Strongs measures need to be taken to provide support to the kids and youth of Victoria since they are the ones who have great potential in shaping the future.

					</p>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<h3 class="t-center p-l-15 p-r-15 p-t-3 title-font" style="color:black; font-size:200%;">
		Distribution of homeless women and men in different accommodations
	</h3>
	<br>

	<!-- 第2行 -->
